<!-- ============ HERO ============ -->
<section class="hero hero--page">
  <div class="hero__bg" aria-hidden="true" data-parallax>
    <!-- PLACEHOLDER: swap for real spa interior photography -->
    <img src="/assets/images/about/about-hero.jpg" alt="" loading="eager" />
  </div>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="hero__content hero__content--center">
      <span class="eyebrow hero__eyebrow" data-reveal="fade">Our Story</span>
      <h1 class="hero__title" data-split-text="immediate">We Are <em>Umoya</em></h1>
      <p class="hero__subhead">Air. Breath. Spirit. A wellness practice built on the belief that real care takes time.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ============ MEANING ============ -->
<section class="section section--dark">
  <div class="container grid-2col">
    <div data-reveal>
      <span class="eyebrow">The Name</span>
      <h2 class="heading-lg" data-split-text>What <em>Umoya</em> Means</h2>
      <p class="text-muted" style="margin-top:1.4rem; max-width:46ch;">Umoya is a Zulu word that holds three meanings at once: air, breath, and spirit. It describes the invisible current that animates everything living: the thing you notice most in its absence.</p>
      <p class="text-muted" style="margin-top:1rem; max-width:46ch;">We chose it because that's what modern life quietly takes from people: room to breathe. Umoya Wellness Spa was designed as the counterweight: a place of lightness, restoration, and quiet luxury where your only job is to exhale.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="img-reveal mask-reveal" data-reveal data-parallax style="aspect-ratio: 4 / 5; border-radius: var(--radius-md);">
      <!-- PLACEHOLDER: swap for real ambient spa photography -->
      <img src="/assets/images/about/meaning.jpg" alt="Soft light and calm textures inside Umoya Wellness Spa" loading="lazy" />
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ============ PHILOSOPHY / WHAT TO EXPECT ============ -->
<section class="section section--light">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-head section-head--center" data-reveal>
      <span class="eyebrow">The Umoya Way</span>
      <h2 class="heading-lg">Clinical Where It Counts. <em>Calm Everywhere Else.</em></h2>
    </div>
    <div class="card-grid" data-reveal-group>
      <div class="text-card">
        <h3 class="text-card__title">Consultation First</h3>
        <p class="text-card__text">Every relationship at Umoya begins with a conversation, not a treatment. We map your goals, your history, and your expectations before anything else, so the plan we build is genuinely yours.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="text-card">
        <h3 class="text-card__title">No Rushed Appointments</h3>
        <p class="text-card__text">You will never feel like a slot on a schedule. Sessions are booked with breathing room, so every treatment gets the time and attention it deserves.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="text-card">
        <h3 class="text-card__title">Honest Expectations</h3>
        <p class="text-card__text">If a treatment isn't right for you, we'll say so. We'd rather set honest expectations and earn your trust than promise results we can't deliver.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="text-card">
        <h3 class="text-card__title">RN-Led, Always</h3>
        <p class="text-card__text">From body contouring to Botox to clinically supervised weight-loss protocols, every service is performed or overseen by a registered nurse with advanced aesthetic training.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ============ FOUNDER BIO ============ -->
<section class="section section--dark">
  <div class="container bio-block" data-reveal>
    <div class="bio-block__portrait img-reveal mask-reveal" data-reveal>
      <img src="/assets/images/about/founder.jpg" alt="Cheryl Johnson, RN-BSN-FAACM, Founder and Wellness Nurse, at Umoya Wellness Spa" loading="lazy" />
    </div>
    <div>
      <span class="eyebrow">Meet the Founder</span>
      <h2 class="heading-lg">Cheryl Johnson</h2>
      <span class="bio-block__credential">RN-BSN-FAACM &middot; Founder &amp; Wellness Nurse</span>

      <p class="text-muted" style="margin-top:1.6rem; max-width:48ch;">Cheryl built Umoya after years of nursing taught her a simple truth: people heal better, and decide better, when they don't feel rushed. As a registered nurse and Fellow of the American Academy of Comprehensive Medicine, she brings clinical rigor to an industry that often runs on hype.</p>
      <p class="text-muted" style="margin-top:1rem; max-width:48ch;">At Umoya, she personally guides every client's plan, from T-Shape 2 body contouring to peptide protocols, with the same standard she'd want for her own family: evidence first, honesty always, and care that never feels clinical-cold.</p>

      <p style="margin-top:1.6rem; max-width:44ch; font-family: var(--font-display); font-style: italic; font-size: 1.15rem; color: var(--gold-300); line-height: 1.55;">"My job isn't to sell you a treatment. It's to tell you the truth about what your body needs, then walk with you while we get there."</p>

      <div style="margin-top:1.8rem; display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:0.6rem;">
        <span class="badge">Body Contouring</span>
        <span class="badge">Medical Weight Loss</span>
        <span class="badge">Injectables &amp; Aesthetics</span>
        <span class="badge">Peptide Therapy</span>
      </div>

      <div class="hero__ctas" style="margin-top:2.2rem;">
        <a href="<%= site.bookingUrl %>" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn btn--primary btn--magnetic" data-cursor="book">Book a Consultation</a>
        <a href="/services" class="link-underline" data-cursor="view">Explore services &rarr;</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ============ FINAL CTA ============ -->
<section class="cta-band cta-band--final">
  <div class="container cta-band__content" data-reveal>
    <span class="eyebrow">Come As You Are</span>
    <h2 class="heading-lg cta-band__title">Experience wellness with <em>room to breathe.</em></h2>
    <a href="<%= site.bookingUrl %>" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn btn--primary btn--magnetic" data-cursor="book">Book Now</a>
  </div>
</section>
